tp://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ABOUT NBCUNIVERSAL  NBCUniversal is one of the world's leading media and entertainment companies in the development, production, and marketing of entertainment, news, sports and information to a global audience.\", \"from\": 4505, \"to\": 4716, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4511, \"end\": 4523, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.9999999988035597, \"rank\": 1.1962724578785454e-09, \"text\": \"NBCUNIVERSAL\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}, {\"begin\": 4525, \"end\": 4537, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.9999999988035597, \"rank\": 1.1962724578785454e-09, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"NBCUniversal owns and operates a valuable portfolio of news and entertainment television networks, a premier motion picture company, significant television production operations, a leading television stations group, world-renowned theme parks, and a premium ad-supported streaming service.\", \"from\": 4717, \"to\": 5006, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4717, \"end\": 4729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.9999999988035597, \"rank\": 1.1962724578785454e-09, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"NBCUniversal is a subsidiary of Comcast Corporation.\", \"from\": 5007, \"to\": 5059, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5007, \"end\": 5019, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.9999999988035597, \"rank\": 1.1962724578785454e-09, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}, {\"begin\": 5039, \"end\": 5058, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Comcast\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Comcast Corporation\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Comcast\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Comcast\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ABOUT TISHMAN SPEYER(tishmanspeyer.com)  Tishman Speyer is a leading owner, developer, operator and investment manager of first-class real estate in 35 key markets across the United States, Europe, Asia and Latin America.\", \"from\": 5061, \"to\": 5282, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5067, \"end\": 5081, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tishman_Speyer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"TISHMAN SPEYER\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tishman_Speyer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tishman_Speyer\"}, {\"begin\": 5102, \"end\": 5116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tishman_Speyer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tishman Speyer\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tishman_Speyer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tishman_Speyer\"}, {\"begin\": 5236, \"end\": 5249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999997908162, \"rank\": 2.0930520941441714e-10, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our portfolio spans market rate and affordable residential communities, premier office properties and retail spaces, industrial facilities, and mixed-use campuses.\", \"from\": 5283, \"to\": 5446, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We create state-of-the-art life science centers through our Breakthrough Properties joint venture, and foster innovation through our strategic proptech investments.\", \"from\": 5447, \"to\": 5611, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With global vision, on-the-ground expertise and a personalized approach, we are unparalleled in our ability to foster innovation, quickly adapt to global and local trends and proactively anticipate our customers' evolving needs.\", \"from\": 5612, \"to\": 5840, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"By focusing on health and wellness, enlightened placemaking and customer-focused initiatives such as our tenant amenities platform, ZO, and our flexible space and co-working brand, Studio, we tend not just to our physical buildings, but to the people who inhabit them on a daily basis.\", \"from\": 5841, \"to\": 6126, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Since our inception in 1978, Tishman Speyer has acquired, developed, and operated 556 properties, totaling 225 million square feet, with a combined value of over $128 billion (U.S.).\", \"from\": 6127, \"to\": 6309, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6156, \"end\": 6170, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tishman_Speyer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tishman Speyer\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tishman_Speyer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tishman_Speyer\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our current portfolio includes such iconic assets as Rockefeller Center in New York City, The Springs in Shanghai, TaunusTurm in Frankfurt and the Mission Rock neighborhood currently being realized in San Francisco.\", \"from\": 6310, \"to\": 6525, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6385, \"end\": 6398, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999999768079, \"rank\": 2.3211697107112668e-11, \"text\": \"New York City\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q4